        "TileImage": "$($repository 579f2544-1970-4865-afa3-ad4566e5f98d).Image",
        "Description": "This test is based on the authentic 1950s mission set in Cuba where legendary ICA agent Erich Soders killed Soviet spy, Jasper Knight and KGB elite, Cilas Netzke. He has seemingly disappeared without a single trace. Jasper Knight and Cilas Netzke was soon found dead after Soders was long gone.\rICA tests aren&apos;t this hard though. This could only mean-Soders wants you to fail. But based on previous testings, you don&apos;t seem too foreign with completely hostile places.",
